@Svipp.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5087
@jwt_token = your-jwt-token-here

### ============================================
### TESTING GUIDE:
### 1. Først: Registrer en ny bruker (eller logg inn)
### 2. Kopier token fra responsen
### 3. Sett @jwt_token variabelen over til tokenet
### 4. Test beskyttede endepunkter
### ============================================

### POST /api/auth/register - Registrer ny bruker
POST {{Svipp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+47 123 45 678",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### 
# Kopier token fra "token" feltet i responsen og sett det i @jwt_token variabelen over
###

### POST /api/auth/login - Logg inn
POST {{Svipp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### 
# Kopier token fra "token" feltet i responsen og sett det i @jwt_token variabelen over
###

### GET /api/users/me - Hent innlogget bruker (krever JWT token)
GET {{Svipp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users/me
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###

### PUT /api/users/me - Oppdater innlogget bruker
PUT {{Svipp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+47 987 65 432"
}

###

### PUT /api/users/me/password - Endre passord
PUT {{Svipp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users/me/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "currentPassword": "OldPassword123!",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword456!",
  "confirmNewPassword": "NewSecurePassword456!"
}

###

### POST /api/rides/{rideId}/handover-confirmation - Registrer/oppdater digital ansvarsoverførings-sjekk før turstart
POST {{Svipp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/rides/1/handover-confirmation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "customerWillNotDrive": true,
  "keysHandedOver": true,
  "confirmedAt": "2025-12-02T12:00:00Z",
  "confirmedByDriver": "driver-123"
}

###

### GET /api/rides/{rideId}/handover-confirmation - Hent ansvarsoverføringsdetaljer for en tur
GET {{Svipp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/rides/1/handover-confirmation
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###

### POST /api/rides/{rideId}/start - Start tur (krever registrert ansvarsoverføring)
POST {{Svipp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/rides/1/start
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###
